{
  "stem": "1581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then we crept into our bunks and slept like logs, sleeping always on the side because there was no room to stretch out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The nights were bitter cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- if you had to go out, you had to go outside, and being hungry, you had a very full bladder all the time because water was there, and your drank an awful lot of water.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What were the nights life?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we were exhausted from this labor, so we slept.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Seven days a week.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the life there was horrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had our enemies counted out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had, of course, the SS people, who were enemy number one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They couldn't help it, beating-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whenever they could, they hit somebody over the head or hit over the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this hurt, this hurt something awful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you didn't run fast enough, they went after you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And shootings were every day's chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Just to give you an example, there was a time when I had a chance to get some food from the outside-- I'll come to that later-- and I was caught.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was-- there was a deep snow at the time, and I was stood up there, and a guy took his rifle and shot me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't know whether he did it on purpose on not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was glanced in my left temple, and I remember absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I only remember that I fell-- I was told I fell into the snow, and I was in a-- in a puddle of blood.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And rumor went, Nash was killed today, which was nothing unusual because it happened all the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was not a day where not one or two of us were just killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
